{"id":13821,"date":"2022-09-30T10:25:15","date_gmt":"2022-09-30T03:25:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13821"},"modified":"2022-09-30T10:25:15","modified_gmt":"2022-09-30T03:25:15","slug":"hyundai-thanh-cong-viet-nam-to-chuc-thanh-cong-hoi-thi-tay-nghe-toan-quoc-2022","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-thanh-cong-viet-nam-to-chuc-thanh-cong-hoi-thi-tay-nghe-toan-quoc-2022\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c 2022"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y\u00a024 \u2013 25\/09\/2022 v\u1eeba qua, Li\u00ean doanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c\u00a0H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng 2022 &#8211; Hyundai Thanh Cong Skill Contest t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p>Ng\u00e0y\u00a024 \u2013 25\/09\/2022 v\u1eeba qua, Li\u00ean doanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c\u00a0H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng 2022 &#8211; Hyundai Thanh Cong Skill Contest t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundai-api.thanhcong.vn\/storage\/uploads\/editors\/2022\/09\/30\/HTTN1.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" \/><br \/>\n<i>\u1ea2nh c\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh \u0111\u1ebfn tham gia H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng 2022.<\/i>\n<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1\u00a0Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng 2022 l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0\u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3\u00a0c\u1ee7a Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV), nh\u1eb1m\u00a0\u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean\u00a0\u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd c\u00f3 k\u1ef9\u00a0n\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean to\u00e0n h\u1ec7\u00a0th\u1ed1ng; h\u01b0\u1edbng\u00a0\u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1\u00a0ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5\u00a0kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. H\u1ed9i thi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i b\u1ed5\u00a0\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean tr\u00ean to\u00e0n b\u1ed9\u00a0h\u1ec7\u00a0th\u1ed1ng\u00a0\u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd c\u00f3 c\u01a1\u00a0h\u1ed9i\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao l\u01b0u, h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundai-api.thanhcong.vn\/storage\/uploads\/editors\/2022\/09\/30\/HTTN2.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" \/><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><i>\u1ea2nh ph\u1ea7n thi l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/i><\/p>\n<p>Cu\u1ed9c thi\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1\u00a0quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 tham d\u1ef1\u00a0c\u1ee7a\u00a0Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch HTV \u2013 \u00d4ng Oh In Won v\u00e0 T\u1ed5ng Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c HTV \u2013 \u00d4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Anh T\u00fa, Ph\u00f3 T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c HTV &#8211; \u00d4ng Ng\u00f4 Ti\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ea1t c\u00f9ng 194 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd tr\u00ean to\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundai-api.thanhcong.vn\/storage\/uploads\/editors\/2022\/09\/30\/HTTN3.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" \/><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><i>\u1ea2nh ph\u1ea7n thi th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean s\u1eefa ch\u1eefa chung.<\/i><\/p>\n<p>H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng 2022\u00a0c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a\u00a0271 th\u00ed sinh, \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 69 \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1edbi\u00a0ph\u1ea7n thi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m 04 n\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0\u00a0sau:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>C\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa chung.<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng thi tay ngh\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, H\u1ed9i thi c\u00f3 c\u00e1c\u00a0ho\u1ea1t\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0\u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c\u00a0v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n\u00a0\u0111em\u00a0\u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh\u00a0nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00fa v\u1ecb\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0\u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb\u00a0t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee7\u00a0\u0111\u00f4 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0:\u00a0Ph\u1ea7n thi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ed9i thi, Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tham quan H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111ua xe Go Kart.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundai-api.thanhcong.vn\/storage\/uploads\/editors\/2022\/09\/30\/HTTN4.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" \/><\/figure>\n<p><i>\u1ea2nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 th\u00ed sinh tham gia\u00a0H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng 2022.<\/i><\/p>\n<p>Sau 2 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25\/09, HTV t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c L\u1ec5 trao gi\u1ea3i H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng 2022 t\u1ea1i\u00a0Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Grand Plaza, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Anh T\u00fa &#8211; T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>Th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Anh T\u00fa vinh danh \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i thi v\u00e0 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/p>\n<p>L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o HTV \u0111\u00e3 trao hoa, c\u00fap v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi 36 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ph\u1ea7n thi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundai-api.thanhcong.vn\/storage\/uploads\/editors\/2022\/09\/30\/HTTN5.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" \/><\/figure>\n<p><i>\u1ea2nh Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o HTV v\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng.<\/i><\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n &amp; t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i H\u1ed9i thi tay ngh\u1ec1 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng 2022.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-thanh-cong-viet-nam-to-chuc-thanh-cong-hoi-thi-tay-nghe-toan-quoc-2022\/screenshot-2022-09-30-102309\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13822\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13822\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screenshot-2022-09-30-102309.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"928\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screenshot-2022-09-30-102309.jpg 928w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screenshot-2022-09-30-102309-300x114.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screenshot-2022-09-30-102309-768x291.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 928px) 100vw, 928px\" \/><\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-thanh-cong-viet-nam-to-chuc-thanh-cong-hoi-thi-tay-nghe-toan-quoc-2022\/screenshot-2022-09-30-102239\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13823\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13823 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screenshot-2022-09-30-102239.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"933\" height=\"641\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screenshot-2022-09-30-102239.jpg 933w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screenshot-2022-09-30-102239-300x206.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Screenshot-2022-09-30-102239-768x528.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 933px) 100vw, 933px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-thanh-cong-viet-nam-to-chuc-thanh-cong-hoi-thi-tay-nghe-toan-quoc-2022\/screenshot-2022-09-30-102224\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13824\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13824 size-full\" src=\"http